@@yMidgaard@@N maintaining its eastern commitment and @@yKowloon@@N honoring
its northern patrols. If either city's attention drifts -- and
Midgaard's attention @@rdoes@@N drift, as Sepulchur Pasture and the
Eccentric Woodland demonstrate -- the Covenant becomes a sealed
